[I] A modern, secure and open-source password manager

[T] KeePassXC is a password manager that stores and manages your most
[T] sensitive information. It is for people with extremly high demands
[T] of secure personal data management.

[U] https://github.com/keepassxreboot/keepassxc

[A] The KeePassXC team
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/security
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
